@1160 = ~Belt~
@1161 = ~Belt of Starshaping~
@1162 = ~This belt was once used by Stinna Raonar, an elven oracle that decided that she no longer wants to see how future may unfold, but that she wants to shape it. To do so, she started to learn how to change the future and manipulate the power of luck.

